Snippets for solving simple issues in Woocommerce, wordpress, and other settings. 

*INDEX*

unset_shipping_method -
	
	Add this function to your functions.php file in wordpress to unset a shipping method when other methods become available. Useful for setting up promo shipping for single/sample items. 


toggle_radio_options - 
	
	This code will allow you to open up different options based on which radio button a user selects. 


equalize_column_heights -

	this code equalizes the height of various items in a column. Add the styles to your styles.css file, and replace your woocommerce price.php file with the rest of the code. This will require tweaking for your site. 